  "title": "BIM Coordinator ",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p>a) Report to the Manager/Team leader as shown in the organization chart. Responsible for the coordination and control of technical matters, quality implementation and site supervision works.</p>\n<p>b) The detailed duties and responsibilities includes but not limited to the following:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with all the parties including sub-contractors and consultants to solve and coordinate technical issues.</li>\n  <li>Production and maintaining of drawings from BIM (Revit) model and ensure proper transmission of data to all parties involved.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the detailed schedules of drawing production and site progress are met.</li>\n  <li>For quality management, the coordinator is responsible to fully implement with the quality recordings, carry out result analysis and formulate action plans for continuous improvement.</li>\n  <li>Transform AutoCAD drawings into 3D drawings.</li>\n  <li>Ensure BIM standards and Level of Development (LOD) are followed.</li>\n  <li>Supervise site works according to the quality and EHS requirements.</li>\n  <li>Handle all inspections and handing over process with the final objective of achieving customer satisfaction and high Conquas/QM score.</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc matters as assigned by the PM which is necessary for the execution of the project.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Architecture / Engineering</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2-3 years' experience in BIM Drafting (Architectural or M&amp;E)</li>\n</ul>",
